{"tid":430428,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV宣佈免費播今屆英足盃","createTime":"2017-10-09T18:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T00:05:31.000Z","uid":55981,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71117c8870ffa1ca70a5069d6cef9e0833587fca","tid":430428,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20171010/57311901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20171010%2F57311901&d=4LEb4YyAUYZV8NcSq2UbhgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=260f6227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20171010%2F57311901&h=a4ec4d5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20171010/57311901</a><br />\n<br />\nViuTV周一舉行了2018年節目巡禮，總經理魯庭暉席間宣佈，ViuTV及ViuTVsix已取得2018年英格蘭足總盃的免費電視獨家播映權，是近年少有免費電視購得英足盃的轉播，將會播出當中的30場賽事，更會於中、英文兩台同播。<br />\n<br />\n本來英足盃在香港的獨家播映權，由樂視體育擁有，去年曾宣佈獲2016/17年度起合共三屆英足盃賽事的獨家版權，奈何疑因財困問題，在上屆阿仙奴對車路士的決賽上演前，以節目調整為由放棄直播這場大戰，最後幸由無綫電視臨時搶得播映權，才一解球迷憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n對於ViuTV取得免費播映權，網上討論區有不少人讚好。英足盃會在明年一月上演第三圈賽事，包括曼聯、曼城、車路士及上屆冠軍阿仙奴等列強，都會在此圈亮相。"},{"pid":"b7a7e955f62d80cba7d9676a9f9b7236239f2313","tid":430428,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:55:58.000Z","msg":"逼害游生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37900b9df8322efd60049a3ebdb0b3c031b4a08b","tid":430428,"uid":51951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T23:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逼害游生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n節目巡禮冇我同心美呢啲icon撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bda4dc43ec46b2ac388a07ce212a7f5d76a862","tid":430428,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":